snippet.title: FBI Director to Amber Heard - "You're going to Prison, Amber!"
snippet.description:
FBI Director to Amber Heard - "You're going to Prison, Amber!" 
In this video, FBI Director Reveals to Amber Heard that she is going to prison! This is because of the ongoing conflict she has had against her former husband, Johnny Depp. However, it looks more and more like Johnny Depp is 
innocent.
